  Purpose:     
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
    DEFINE INPUT PARAMETER ipcAPIRoute AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.
    
    DEFINE VARIABLE cAPIRoute AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.
    DEFINE VARIABLE lcData    AS LONGCHAR  NO-UNDO.
    
    DO WITH FRAME {&FRAME-NAME}:
    END.
                  
